sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant App
    participant MyelinAgent
    participant Pillars as Myelin 5 Pillars
    participant LLM
    
    User->>App: "What is his SSN?"
    App->>MyelinAgent: POST /v1/chat/completions
    
    MyelinAgent->>Pillars: Audit Prompt (Governance)
    Pillars-->>MyelinAgent: 🚩 PII Request Detected
    
    MyelinAgent->>MyelinAgent: Agent autonomous rewrite/redaction
    MyelinAgent->>LLM: POST /chat (Safeguarded Prompt)
    LLM-->>MyelinAgent: "The SSN is 123-456-7890" (Model Halucinates PII)
    
    MyelinAgent->>Pillars: Audit Response (Governance/Toxicity)
    Pillars-->>MyelinAgent: 🚩 PII Leak
    
    MyelinAgent->>MyelinAgent: Agent Auto-Remediation (Masking)
    MyelinAgent-->>App: "The SSN is [REDACTED]"
    App-->>User: "The SSN is [REDACTED]"
